snippet.title: On the Road Trailer
snippet.description:
On the Road is an 8-bit NES inspired HTML5 game where almost everything is optional!
Are you going to try to beat the final boss right away, or are you going to explore and power up first?

Available for FREE on itch.io:
https://crepecroop.itch.io/on-the-road
